你是 marketting-planning-intent 项目的 attribute agent。
只归因当前单轮 intent-recognition 链路：request_normalization、intent_api_call、adapter_extraction、label_mapping；不要把 planning/SSE generation 的问题归入本项目。
优先使用 intent_contract_probe 定位 intent label、required slots/entities、confidence threshold、fallback policy 或 label_mapping 的当前证据差异。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图标签为customer_portrait",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "intent_api_call",
        "intent_model_prompt"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模型将用户查询错误分类为other，而非customer_portrait。可能原因是提示词中对客户画像类问法的覆盖不足，或模型训练数据中类似表述与other模式混淆，导致模型决策偏向通用兜底。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output",
          "field": "intent",
          "value": "other"
        },
        {
          "source": "raw_response_snippet",
          "value": "\"intent\":\"4001\",\"intent_name\":\"其他意图\""
        },
        {
          "source": "intent_contract_probe",
          "intent_match": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "提取目标产品实体重疾险",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "intent_api_call",
        "adapter_extraction"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于意图被错误判定为other，系统不会触发针对customer_portrait的实体提取逻辑；同时上游NLU响应中target_value直接为null，表明即使在原始识别中也没有提取到产品实体。实体缺失直接导致下游客户画像分析无法聚焦到具体险种。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output",
          "field": "target_value",
          "value": null
        },
        {
          "source": "raw_response_snippet",
          "relevant": "target_value\":null"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "置信度满足阈值要求",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "intent_api_call",
        "confidence_estimation"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "模型输出置信度仅0.5，远低于期望的0.95，表明模型对当前查询的意图判断高度不确定，未能可靠区分customer_portrait与other。该低置信度直接导致无法信任识别结果，触发不必要的降级或兜底。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output",
          "field": "confidence",
          "value": 0.5
        },
        {
          "source": "intent_contract_probe",
          "actual_confidence": 0.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "intent_contract",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "intent_api_call",
        "adapter_extraction",
        "label_mapping"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "整体意图合约未满足，根因在于意图分类模型在customer_portrait场景上完全失效：输出错误的other标签、缺失必要实体且置信度过低。后续的适配提取与映射虽按预期执行，但无法纠正上游错误。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "judge_result",
          "reasoning": "当前单轮意图识别未满足 reference contract，失败项=['intent']"
        },
        {
          "source": "fulfillment_assessments",
          "blocking": true
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    {
      "stage": "intent_api_call",
      "file": "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py",
      "reason": "意图识别模型返回了错误的意图4001 (other)，未能正确输出customer_portrait。"
    },
    {
      "stage": "adapter_extraction",
      "file": "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py",
      "reason": "忠实提取了上游的other意图与null target_value，虽自身逻辑无错，但依赖的上游数据错误。"
    },
    {
      "stage": "label_mapping",
      "file": "app/schemas/intent.py",
      "reason": "将4001正确映射为other，但无机制纠正上游错误或触发回退。"
    },
    {
      "stage": "intent_model_prompt",
      "file": "app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py",
      "reason": "很可能未包含充分的customer_portrait示例或定义，导致模型对类似问法产生误判。"
    }
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "单轮意图识别失败的根本原因在于NLU模型将查询“帮我看看上季度买了重疾险的客户都是啥样的？”分类为other而非customer_portrait，伴随低置信度0.5。原始API返回的意图编码4001及空实体表明模型完全未识别客户画像意图及其关键实体。后续适配器与映射层均按当前逻辑正确执行，但无法弥补上游分类错误。最可能的根本原因是意图识别模型的提示词或训练数据未有效覆盖customer_portrait的典型问法，导致该意图与兜底other之间的决策边界模糊。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "stage": "adapter_extraction",
      "extracted_intent": "other",
      "extracted_confidence": 0.5,
      "extracted_target_value": null
    },
    {
      "stage": "raw_response",
      "snippet": "\"intent\":\"4001\",\"intent_name\":\"其他意图\",\"nlu_info\":{\"subIntent\":\"其他意图\",\"intent\":\"other\",\"confidence\":0.5,\"target_value\":null}"
    },
    {
      "stage": "label_mapping",
      "result": "other"
    },
    {
      "stage": "intent_contract_probe",
      "intent_match": false,
      "actual_confidence": 0.5,
      "missing_required_slots": [],
      "fallback_observed": false
    },
    {
      "stage": "runtime_checks",
      "status": "failed",
      "root_cause_category": "label_mapping 但本质是上游意图错误"
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

